reviews.name: Lim T
reviews.text: 以上的图片是我让医生给我重新修补了第二次的 第一次的真的糟糕透顶丑到半死 不懂这个是门牙一样 没有形状理念就不要做人家的门牙 我平时也不是那么计较的人 这家牙科是第一个 还有我后面的牙齿本来不痛的给他补下第二天睡觉被痛醒 我严重怀疑她没有清理干净 我也是第一次看到补牙不用水冲洗 第一次帮我补的牙齿那个形状真的难以想象还是门牙 上面凹进去 下面又很凸出来 然后上面还没磨好还翘起来 里面有很小的缝没有填满 就好像只是被一块塑料包裹着一样丑陋 后面的牙我还没有什么 但是是门牙 已经严重影响我的自信 笑容 然后坑坑洼洼的非常的粗糙技术 然后我让她再重新补第二次 修复 还是不完美不好看 她就语气不耐烦对顾客态度语气也很不好 我非常不满意也不敢再给他做并停止了 然后事后我和我母亲说要给她差评 她听到还威胁我说如果影响到她的生意 她便会采取法律行动 作为你的顾客 给你钱赚态度还能这么恶劣 顾客不满完全推销责任全程没有道歉 只说自己有服务了 可是问题是医生的技术有问题还不让顾客说了 她叫我进去做到我满意 我想说的是你的技术根本就不到位 做再久你也做不出来 只会让牙齿二次损伤 作为一名医师 连最基本的职业素质心理都没有 还出来做服务业 我在那里哭了她还是一样态度很恶劣 不停狡辩觉得自己没有问题 态度也很强势 只能自叹倒霉 之前遇到的从来都没有这样过的 无论态度还是技术她也一点都不细心3颗牙齿不到20分钟就完成 没有第二次 我觉得她也没有清理到很干净 和我之前在别家相比 非常无敌糟糕的体验 甚至让我对以后去看牙医的心理有阴影了 后面她跟我妈妈沟通 我觉得她说的不合理 变反驳 她还很大声跟我说我在跟你妈妈讲话 我跟你讲话了吗 作为一名医生居然能这样对顾客  技术完全不行新开张才两年垃圾技术毫无经验 毫无耐心 毫无职业心理素质 钱还招收一句道歉没有....我各人认为遇过最糟糕的牙医没有之一👎🏻👎🏻
reviews.textTranslated: 1、你的牙齊的牙齊的牙齊的牙齊的牙齊的牙齊的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的牙齊 的The customer was dissatisfied and she took all the responsibility. She didn't apologize at all. She just said that she had provided the service. However, the problem was that the doctor's technique had problems and she didn't let the customer speak out. She asked me to go in and do it until I was satisfied. What I want to say is that your technique is not up to par at all. You can't do it well no matter how long you work on it. It will only cause secondary damage to the teeth. As a doctor, you don't even have the most basic professional quality and mentality, and you still come out to work in the service industry. I cried there, but she still had a very bad attitude. She kept quibbling and felt that she had no problem. Her attitude was also very strong. I could only sigh that I had bad luck. I had never encountered such a person before. She was not careful at all in terms of attitude or technique. It took less than 20 minutes to finish 3 teeth. There was no second time. I think she didn't clean them very well. Compared with my previous experience at other dentists, it was an extremely bad experience. It even traumatized me psychologically about going to the dentist in the future. Later, she communicated with my mother. I felt that what she said was unreasonable and turned to refute. She also said to me loudly, "I'm talking to your mother. Did I talk to you?" As a doctor, she can actually treat customers like this. Her technique is completely bad. The business has only been open for two years. She has rubbish technique, no experience, no patience, and no professional mentality. I didn't even ask for an apology...I personally think this is the worst dentist I've ever met👎🏻👎🏻

reviews.name: Skype He
reviews.text: 这是一个非常糟糕的体验。只能说牙医的技术还需提升。第一回补牙补到坑坑洞洞，由于不满意，要求牙医修补，结果牙医开始态度改变了，补了第二次，结果还是那样，不能让人满意。于是失去了对牙医的信心，失望透顶，便告之别补了。因为是门牙，所以既生气又頽丧，便打算给牙医差评。孰不知牙医得知后，竟声明若做了会影响她生意的举动，她不排除会采取法律的行动对付。她说这句话的意思是什么？服务不满意，顾客不能给差评了？这是要顾客委屈求全，唾面自干？我真的很无语，连个差评，说真话，表达自己的经验感受都被禁止了？那这个平台的评价的用途是什么？本来想息事宁人，结果因为牙医的一句话，就不想妥协了。顾客的难受，无助，哭泣，她会知道吗？当初就是奔5颗星去的，结果。。。只能自叹倒霉，花钱买气受。。。
reviews.textTranslated: This is a very bad experience. I can only say that the dentist's skills need to be improved. The first time I filled a tooth, there was a hole. I was not satisfied and asked the dentist to fix it. As a result, the dentist's attitude changed. I filled it for the second time, but the result was still the same and unsatisfactory. So I lost confidence in the dentist and was extremely disappointed, so I told him not to fill it again. Because it was a front tooth, I was angry and depressed, so I planned to give the dentist a bad review. Little did I know that after the dentist learned about it, she stated that if she did anything that would affect her business, she would not rule out taking legal action. What does she mean by saying this? If the customer is not satisfied with the service, the customer cannot give a bad review? Is this asking the customer to compromise and swallow the spit? I am really speechless. Even giving a bad review, telling the truth, and expressing one's own experience and feelings are prohibited? Then what is the purpose of the evaluation on this platform? I originally wanted to settle the matter peacefully, but because of the dentist's words, I didn't want to compromise. Will she know the customer's discomfort, helplessness, and crying? I went there for 5 stars, but the result... I can only sigh that I am unlucky and spend money to get angry...

reviews.name: Kelvin Wong
reviews.text:
以个人的经历分享下在此诊所进行的几项治疗：

1. 门牙崩掉因为相当紧急，问了多间牙医的预约都需要到好几个星期后～在透过家人的介绍下，就抱着试试的心情私聊这间诊所，很快就得到了回复明天就可以安排帮我检查～期间我也问了治疗项目的价钱那些，回复者也相当有礼貌地一一告知～

2. 来到此诊所后，柜台服务员态度也非常好地问候和帮我注册填写资料和详细了解目前所服用的药物和药物敏感那些～整间店的环境简洁舒适，重点是医生也准时到达，因为当天我是第一个接受治疗的～推门见到医生时，医生礼貌地安排我躺下后，便简单地介绍下自己和确认下我当天预约的治疗项目～在医生相当娴熟的操作下，不到十分钟就帮我把崩掉的门牙给填补好了～经此一役后我对这医生就相当有信心，也非常满意他的服务态度～于是我就进一步询问他关于我其他颗牙齿的治疗方式，医生二话不说帮我进行了检查,也针对每一颗牙齿给出了建议和解决方案～而我接下来要做的一系列治疗就是补一颗牙、拔掉一颗蛀牙，最重要的就是我遗憾和自卑很久的一颗丢失的前牙（在门牙的右边），相当影响美观，也让我几十年都不敢张口笑...医生给我的建议就是戴假牙套或者造一副牙桥，但不建议我植牙因为怕牙骨会因空间太小而撑爆掉～他也没让我立刻做决定，而是给出几个建议让我回去考虑下～那戴假牙套就相当麻烦要脱下戴上的，而且会不自然的感觉～那就只是牙桥这种了，可以直接黏死不需要脱下，所以我回去后直接果断又信息他们直接预约安排时间同时补牙、拔牙和做牙桥～

3. 到了隔天预约的时间，我一到就被安排见医生了～带着还是非常紧张的心情，因为还是会怕拔牙会很痛...医生安慰说他们会确保麻醉了才进行所以别担心～首先，补牙还是相当快不到十分钟就完成，到了拔牙时可能因为蛀牙比较深的关系，我看医生相当地忙拿这个拿那个在我嘴里飞快地操作着～当下的我还是默默地闭起了双眼，老实说因为张着嘴巴太久整个下巴真的酸死了，但是谢天谢地整个过程都不痛，只是稍微有些感觉～下一步就到那缺牙的地方进行一系列的修牙、scan、拿模型样本～完成一系列的治疗也差不多一个小时左右而已～然后被告知隔天就可以拿到我的牙桥和进行安装了，速度之快让我感到诧异～

4. 终于儞补了我那颗牙齿丢失的遗憾，让我重新获得能够开怀大笑的信心～真心感谢这位耐心又友善且年轻有为的医生，愿你前程似锦且能继续帮助更多有需要的人～也希望看到此文的人，可以帮助到你们更多了解和放心交给此医生帮你们安排与解决你们的难题～
reviews.textTranslated:
Let me share some of the treatments performed at this clinic based on my personal experience:

1. The collapse of my front teeth was quite urgent, so I asked several dentists to make an appointment for several weeks. After being introduced by my family, I privately chatted with this clinic with the intention of giving it a try. I quickly received a reply that they would arrange a check-up for me tomorrow. During this period, I also asked about the prices of the treatment items, and the responders also informed me politely.

2. After arriving at this clinic, the counter staff greeted me very well and helped me register and fill in the information and learn more about the drugs I am currently taking and those I am sensitive to. The environment of the whole store is simple and comfortable. The important thing is that the doctor arrived on time, because I was the first to receive treatment that day. When I opened the door to see the doctor, the doctor politely arranged for me to lie down, and then briefly introduced himself and confirmed The treatment I made an appointment for that day~ Under the doctor's very skillful operation, he helped me fill in the chipped front teeth in less than ten minutes. After this battle, I was quite confident in the doctor and very satisfied with his service attitude~ So I further asked him about the treatment methods for my other teeth. The doctor checked me without saying a word and gave me advice on each tooth. Suggestions and solutions ~ The next series of treatments I have to do are to fill a tooth and remove a cavity. The most important thing is a missing front tooth (on the right side of the front tooth) that I have regretted and felt inferior to for a long time. It greatly affects the appearance and makes me dare not open my mouth to smile for decades... The doctor’s advice to me is to wear dentures or build a dental bridge, but he does not recommend dental implants because I am afraid of the bone. It would burst because the space was too small~ He didn't let me make a decision right away, but gave me some suggestions to go back and think about it~ Wearing dentures is very troublesome, I have to take them off and put them on, and it will feel unnatural~ It's just a dental bridge.

3. When the appointment time arrived the next day, I was scheduled to see the doctor~ I was still very nervous, because I was still afraid that tooth extraction would be very painful... The doctor reassured me that they would ensure anesthesia before proceeding, so don't worry~ First of all, the tooth filling was completed very quickly in less than ten minutes. When it came time to extract the tooth, it might be because of the deep cavities. I saw the doctor who was very busy, quickly operating this and that in my mouth~ At the moment, I was still I closed my eyes silently. To be honest, my whole jaw was really sore from keeping my mouth open for so long. But thankfully, the whole process was not painful, I just felt a little bit. The next step was to go to the missing tooth area for a series of teeth repairs, scans, and model samples. It took about an hour to complete a series of treatments. Then I was told that my dental bridge could be received and installed the next day. I was surprised by how fast it was.

4. Finally, my missing tooth was repaired and I regained the confidence to laugh. I sincerely thank this patient, friendly and young and promising doctor. I wish you a bright future and can continue to help more people in need. I also hope that those who read this article can help you understand more and trust this doctor to help you arrange and solve your problems.

reviews.responseFromOwnerText: 非常谢谢你的反应，让我们知道这个问题，我们先说声抱歉，如果有让你不满意的地方。这里我们按照我们的立场做一些解释：最近确实有一个顾客来这里补牙，不过不是rynie sia这个名字。当时补的是上面左右各最后一个的智慧牙的咬合面，并不是接近牙龈的地方。补好好牙医也有询问咬合是否ok，顾客回答ok，牙医才让顾客离开。过几天顾客告知我们补牙的地方痛，所以我们就询问顾客是否有补太高的情况，对方回复是，于是我们立刻安排顾客回来磨掉一点补牙材料，看看会不会缓解咬力的压力。对不起我们并不知道你主要的问题是牙龈发炎，因为我们问的时候，对方并没指明牙龈发炎。如果牙医知道的话，会试着帮你那个部位的牙龈清洗和给消炎药，因为有时候智慧牙很难清理，也有可能造成牙龈发炎。无论如何，我们都献上我们的道歉，若你愿意回来查看，我们会用最大诚意来帮助你解决问题，再次的谢谢你。至于如果你觉得牙医的态度恶劣，牙医也深深献上歉意，牙医在每一个顾客进来都会向顾客问好，而服务好每个顾客都会说声谢谢，牙医也记得他当天并没有用不好的语气和顾客对话，当天他就是立刻安排顾客回来，想办法解决问题。再次献上最大的歉意和谢谢你的批评，我们会更加进步。

The root of the tooth remains inside.
It took me four hours of surgery in a government hospital to clean my teeth.
